{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_07_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 今も、そしてこれからも戦い続ける",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――映画の撮影が終了し、数日経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days after the filming ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、今日は映画の宣伝ポスターの撮影だよね\nどうしてカメラを回してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ we’re shooting the promotional poster for the movie today‚ right?\nWhy are you filming?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.9948067505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "メイキング動画の撮影もやるそうだ\nインタビューもあるから、真面目に答えてくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re filming a behind the scene video too.\nYou’ll be interviewed‚ so answer seriously‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4581397215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕はいつだって真面目なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4581397215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "真面目にとんでもないことを言い出すんだった……\n分かったよ、いざとなったら俺がフォローする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say the most ridiculous things with a straight face…\nOkay‚ I’ll back you up if need be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7666664918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.5736049016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、信じてるよ、{user}君\n……あ、そろそろ始まるみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I trust you‚ {user}.\n…Ah‚ it looks like it’s starting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4031511624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、撮影はもちろん大変だったけど\nそれ以上に楽しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ filming was tough‚ of course‚\nbut it was also a lot of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、僕も原作のファンだからね\n自分なりに噛み砕いて、全力で表現したつもりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I’m a fan of the original story.\nI tried to break down the role in my own way and express it with all my might.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1333268006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.7740970294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（あの後も、葵とは演技の練習のためにいろいろやった）\n（……けど、あまり役には立てなかった気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We did a lot of things together for Aoi’s acting practice after that…）\n（…but I don’t think I was much help.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.266660134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（でも葵の演技は見事だった。一度やると決めたことは）\n（必ずやる……その約束を完璧に守ってくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ Aoi’s acting was amazing. When she sets her mind to something‚）\n（she always follows through… She kept her promise perfectly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9999934673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4853891056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "演技をしてるつもりはそんなにないよ。歌やダンス\nみたいに、表現したっていう方がしっくりくるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t really think of it as acting. It’s more like…\nI expressed myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.566660134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.1593845368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、あえて言うなら、僕のわがままを聞いて\nどんな練習でも付き合ってくれる人がいるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if I had to say‚ there’s someone who listens to my whims\nand practices with me‚ no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7333313782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "もし良く出来てたなら\nきっとその人のおかげだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I did well‚\nit’s definitely thanks to that person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6333308696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5587470373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "かなり振り回されたが、また一歩踏み出せたみたいだな\nこれなら、ポスターの撮影も安心して見ていられそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I put them through a lot‚ but it seems like I’ve taken another step forward.\nWith this‚ I can watch the poster shoot without worrying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333288351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "このセット、いいね。映画のラストシーンを\n撮影してた時のことを思い出すな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like this set. It reminds me\nof when we were filming the last scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0999955017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "葵、撮影に集中してくれ。カメラに目線を送って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ focus on the shoot. Look at the camera.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.931535848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごめん。これでいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry. Like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3715369225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "役を演じた時の表情を作ってほしいそうだけど\nその場面、思い出せるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want you to make the same expression as when you were\nplaying the character‚ but can you remember that scene?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8999955017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "印象的なセリフがあったから、覚えてるよ\n主人公と対峙して、戦う直前に僕が言うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a memorable line‚ so I remember.\nI say it right before I fight against the protagonist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.899996519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "出会い方が違ったら\n友達になれたかもしれないね、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we had met under different circumstances‚\nmaybe we could have been friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7999924499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら、彼女はこう言うんだ\n私は今でも友達だと思ってる、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ she says:\nI still consider you a friend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3999741393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "友達とでも、時には戦わなきゃならない\nそれを受け入れている彼女の気持ちが、僕には分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even friends have to fight sometimes.\nI understand how she feels‚ accepting that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9999710875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとしてだけど、僕は星見プロの親しい人達と\n競い合って、戦ってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As an idol‚ I've competed and fought alongside the people\nclose to me at Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8333003519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "今も、そしてこれからも\n戦い続けることになるだろうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fighting now‚ and I’ll continue to fight\nin the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.5332759378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――映画公開から少し経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the movie was released",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2354623396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 164.8354775984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "僕に？　また演技の仕事？\n映画に出演しただけでそんなことになるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me? Another acting job?\nThat’s what happens just from being in a movie?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5666174091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "出演しただけじゃない\n葵の演技が評価されたからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not just because you appeared in it.\nIt’s because your acting was praised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.733285093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
